{"tid":851350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李力持作詩寸爆絕食學生","createTime":"2018-10-07T05:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T01:08:09.000Z","uid":30788,"like":30,"dislike":524,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"522ceab333d57516c44b5d871d25a68486239af7","tid":851350,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:21:03.000Z","msg":"理大日前發生學渣禁錮師長事件，學渣還不知悔改，昨晚突然發難，話要絕食明志喎！對此，名導李力持為一班廢青學生作了首詩，大加嘲諷！<br />\n<br />\n李力持在其Facebook分享了相關新聞，留言以一首「啜核」的詩句串爆絕食學渣︰傻仔廢青話絕食，唔通又係玩接力，<br />\n呢招真白痴到極，弱智低能真無敵！<br />\n正宗廢柴無很用，自取其辱被利用，<br />\n有書唔讀搞暴動，燒壞個腦忘祖宗！李導認真句句金句！<br />\n<br />\n李導咁有創意，當然獲得許多網民大讚，更有網民表示學生所為只是「有鏡頭有目光之下絕食啫」、「四小時絕一次，以不同人接力絕食&hellip;」<br />\n李導不平則鳴，絕對抵讚啦！"},{"pid":"8873333a533023045d04f5adc485a77bd1e431fe","tid":851350,"uid":13504,"like":402,"dislike":3,"score":399,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"...佢都係返返自己個年代啦..."},{"pid":"5bc562a0a5e369f9001d6e4411049ff9b8cbf9f5","tid":851350,"uid":187227,"like":306,"dislike":2,"score":304,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"感謝李生解決全球暖化問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd828568f73371e936ef077edc43e467e0e4cf33","tid":851350,"uid":125434,"like":132,"dislike":1,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"呢條傻尻真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21b3b6ce371caa7b9e113114ec7006f0222582d","tid":851350,"uid":63843,"like":227,"dislike":4,"score":223,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"小學雞格硬為押韻作果d垃圾詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a975353e295caf2d8c3e0027b6ae721b2d40d73","tid":851350,"uid":51039,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"笑話星人又出嚟"},{"pid":"af7f